reviewText: This turned out to be a great inexpensive add on to get my "free super saver shipping" I wasn't exactly falling out of my chair with laughs but definitely got a few chuckles out of it, and I enjoy seeing all the old 50s and 60s clips they are comical by themselves, the DVD has a really long runtime of 96mins so it's a lot of content basically MST3K style for only 3 bucks, I'm happy I added it to my order and will likely get a good deal of replay value out of it.
